    <h2 class="text-header is-marged-bottom is-before-text">What is Simple Start?</h1>
    <p class="text-body is-lead is-marged-bottom is-between-sections">Simple Start is a easy and fast way for kickstarting various projects. It contains the bear minimun of core features in order to start a project. 
    <br>
    Simple Starts guarantees you a consistent and scalable approach for making systems and pages.
    <br>
    It uses the mobile first approach to ensure that every component will be mobile friendly.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-header is-marged-bottom is-before-text">Core features</h1>
    <p class="text-body is-lead is-marged-bottom is-between-sections">Simple Start's main features are color definitions, responsive typography and spacings. This is the base of every project and it is essentials to be set properly in order to be scaleble and reuable.</p>

    <h2 class="text-header is-marged-bottom is-before-text">How to install it?</h1>
    <p class="text-body is-lead is-marged-bottom is-between-sections">Clone the projects from the repository, install its dependencies and run it. Simple as that :)</p>

    <h2 class="text-header is-marged-bottom is-before-text">How to use it?</h1>
    <h3 class="text-title is-marged-bottom is-before-text">Define your main colors</h3>
    <p class="text-body is-lead is-marged-bottom">Start with the primary and secondary colors. Define colors for success, error, warning and info. You will need some neutral color scheem (gray nuances). For more info check <a href="#" target="_blank">these articles</a>.</p>

    <h3 class="text-title is-marged-bottom is-before-text">Define your typography</h3>
    <p class="text-body is-lead is-marged-bottom is-between-sections">Define how many title, header and body text are you going to use. Keep the number small and consistent.</p>

